Examples

Method run example

The following example presents how to run the method:

The data files

Two files were inserted, one for cytokine measurments and another for outcome measurments. The files can be seen in the method git repository

The parameters

Project Name was set as "Example", Compartment was set as "Plasma", Luminex and Log transformation were not marked, Max K was set to 6 clusters, Age was defined as a Covariate and was log transformed, outcomes 1-3 were chosen for the analysis, all cytokines were analyzed.

The Results

The results can be seen in the Results tab using the ID: fc9ac628-bb13-11ea-a20f-0242ac120002
